title: Phil Morwood
text: Phil Morwood born 17 June 1982 in <a href="Toowoomba%2C%20Queensland">Toowoomba, Queensland</a>, Australia is a former professional <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> footballer who played for the <a href="Manly%20Sea%20Eagles">Manly Sea Eagles</a> in the <a href="National%20Rugby%20League">National Rugby League</a>.
